==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: /hōld/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /həʊld/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /h@Uld/

=== Verb ===
'''to hold''' ([[held]], [[holds]], [[holding]])
# to [[grasp]] or [[grip]]
#: ''Hold the pencil like this.''
# to [[contain]] or [[store]]
#: ''This package holds six bottles.'' 
# to have and keep [[possess]]ion of something
#: ''Hold my coat for me.''
# to [[reserve]]
#: ''Hold a table for us at 7:00.''
# to [[wait]] or [[delay]]
#: ''Hold the elevator.''
# to [[detain]]
#: ''Hold the suspect in this cell.''

